snippet.title: Atlas Rogues - Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
gamigo's continuation of the Atlas saga, Atlas Rogues, will launch in Early Access on Steam and Glyph on November 18! Players will be able to prove their tactical skills in thrilling, turn-based single-player or co-op matches and participate in challenging missions.
Learn more: https://www.atlasrogues.com
